        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/97f17d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-01-06T21:07:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I still have some 2007s \u2013 I paid $45 a bottle. I buy this almost every vintage, but $85 for the 2015s is starting to get a little crazy. That said, I look forward to trying and would be surprised if a Fourrier would resemble a big west coast pinot.</p>",
